3. Usage/Activation Steps
Reload systemd:
sudo systemctl daemon-reload

Enable auto-start for each service:
sudo systemctl enable breadcount-ros2 breadcount-main breadcount-uvicorn

Start each service:
sudo systemctl start breadcount-ros2 breadcount-main breadcount-uvicorn

Check status/logs:

Service status: sudo systemctl status breadcount-main
View logs: journalctl -u breadcount-main.service -f